These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, tiparillo, bluemaster, baccarat
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, r&b, salsa, techno
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, indonesian, polish
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, tram, trike
1. the colombian is the fan of techno##1
2. the indonesian is between the bluemaster-smoker and the baccarat-smoker##2
3. the colombian is the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left of the canadian##1
6. the person driving the tram is the bluemaster-smoker##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
8. the canadian is on the far right##1
9. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Cigar   | tiparillo | baccarat   | vegafina  | bluemaster  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | techno    | metal      | salsa    |
| Nationality   | polish | colombian | indonesian | canadian |
| Transport     | trike  | bus       | jet-ski    | tram     |

