.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, blueberry, lemon, mango
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, fishing, photography, traveling
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, september, april, july
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, subway
1. the person who's birthday is in april is the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
7. the person eating mango is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
8. the person eating artichoke is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
9. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person eating lemon and the person who's birthday is in september##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | blueberry | lemon     | artichoke   | mango     |
| Hobby       | fishing   | camping   | photography | traveling |
| Birthday         | march   | april | july       | september    |
| Transport   | roller    | motorbike | helicopter  | subway    |

