.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
House: colonial, palace, wooden, tower
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, martial-arts, scientific
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, hamster, pony
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, soccer, volleyball
 1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching scientific movies is the colonial house##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is the owner of the frog##1
 6. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 7. the person watching disaster movies is the wooden house##1
 8. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the colonial house is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
10. the palace house is between the owner of the bird and the tower house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| House           | colonial  | tower | palace     | wooden |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | action  | martial-arts | disaster       |
| Pet           | frog       | pony    | hamster      | bird           |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | rugby   | volleyball   | soccer         |

