5. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person watching documentary movies##2
6. the person playing go is the person watching zombie movies##1
7. the person playing billiard is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
8. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing domino##1

