 2. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 4. the person who's sport is sailing is the person drinking lemonade##1
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 8. the owner of the turtle is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is skiing##2
 9. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is skiing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
