 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 7. the person who's sport is tennis is the colombian##1
 8. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the hamster is the person driving the train##1
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
